text:
Twentieth Ave. (right, not seen), south side, west from 31st Street, showing from fore to background in a set of three views the homes of John Alsop and Peter Rapelje. Note these houses were about 300 feet south of Twentieth Ave. The house in the foreground was demolished in March 1925; the other was not standing in 1927. This is a set of three views. (Old Bowery Road).

March 1923.
Views 1 & 2.
View 3: May 1923.

E. L. Armbruster Collection.
